branchCategory.name: 10-MGF
branchCategory.description: <P>Clean series 10-MGF is a guide table type actuator available in 40, 63 and 100mm bore sizes.  This guide table is a double acting, non-lube type, available with Rc, NPT or G ports.  Particle generation measurement tests classify the 10-MGF clean series as grade 2.  After inspection, the 10-MGF is blown with high purity air (clean bench/class M3.5) in a clean environment.  It is then sealed and shipped in an anti-static double bag.</P>
